    "summary": "quay.io exposes two developer integration surfaces: the Quay REST API at `https://quay.io/api/v1/` authenticated with Quay OAuth access tokens, and the container registry HTTP API at `https://quay.io/v2/` used by Docker-compatible clients with Quay-issued registry credentials (OAuth token via `$oauthtoken`, robot accounts, or deprecated repository access tokens).",
